        <h1>Standard site setup procedures</h1>
        <table style="width: 100%;border-left-color: #000000;border-left-width: 1px;border-right-color: #000000;border-right-width: 1px;background-color: #c0c0c0;border-spacing: 0px;border-spacing: 0px;" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#C0C0C0" width="100%">
            <col style="width: 6.855%;" />
            <col style="width: 93.145%;" />
            <tr valign="top">
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 6.855%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-width: 2px;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-style: Solid;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" valign="middle" width="6.855%">
                    <p class="Note">
                        <img src="../Resources/Images/AAinfo.gif" style="border: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" />
                    </p>
                </td>
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 93.145%;padding-right: 1px;padding-left: 1px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 2px;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" width="93.145%">
                    <p>CAREL devices are controlled by PlantVisorPRO Locale. This type of setup considers all factory device settings.</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <ol style="list-style: decimal;list-style-type: decimal;">
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="1">
                <p class="ActionDetail"><a href="#ConfigurareCampo"> Setting up field devices</a>
                </p>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="2">
                <p class="ActionDetail"><a href="#ProgrammareDispositivi"> Programming devices</a>
                </p>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="3">
                <p class="ActionDetail"><a href="#DefinireUtentiProfili"> Defining users and access profiles</a>
                </p>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="4">
                <p class="ActionDetail"><a href="#ImpostareAttivtaSupervisione"> Setting supervision activities</a>
                </p>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="5">
                <p class="ActionDetail"><a href="#ConfigurareguardianPRO">guardianPRO setup</a>
                </p>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <hr style="color: #808080;height: 1px;float: alignleft;" color="#808080" size="0" align="center" width="100%" />
        <p class="TitoloInterno">
            <img src="../Resources/Images/AAaction.gif" style="border: none;float: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" /><a name="ConfigurareCampo"></a> Setting up field devices</p>
        <ol style="list-style: decimal;list-style-type: decimal;">
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="1">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Declaring devices connected to each serial port
                                                                                                 </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Site configuration</span>, <span style="font-weight: bold;">Add</span> set serial port features. </p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <table style="border-left-color: #000000;border-left-width: 1px;border-right-color: #000000;border-right-width: 1px;background-color: #c0c0c0;width: 90%;margin-left: 40px;border-spacing: 0px;" cellspacing="0" width="90%" bgcolor="#C0C0C0">
                        <col style="width: 6.855%;" />
                        <col style="width: 93.145%;" />
                        <tr valign="top">
                            <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 6.855%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 2px;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" valign="middle" width="6.855%">
                                <p class="Note">
                                    <img src="../Resources/Images/AAinfo.gif" style="border: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;float: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" />
                                </p>
                            </td>
                            <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 93.145%;padding-right: 1px;padding-left: 1px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-width: 2px;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-style: Solid;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" width="93.145%">
                                <p>If a USB-RS485 converter is used, follow the wizard.</p>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>Add physical devices assigning them a serial address</p>
                        </li>
                        <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                            <li class="p" value="1">
                                <p>For CAREL devices, use the <span style="font-weight: bold;">Find device function</span></p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <li class="p" value="2">
                            <p>Edit device descriptions </p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="3">
                            <p>See chapter <a href="Config-sito__dettaglio_linea.htm">Line details.</a></p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="2">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Note any changes made
                                                                                                 </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Site configuration</span>, double-click a line, <span style="font-weight: bold;">Notes</span> add a descriptive note of the completed operations (see chapter <a href="Configurazione__pagina_note.htm">Note page</a>)</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="3">
                <p class="ActionDetail">(optional) Disabling a device</p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Site configuration</span>, double-click a line, <span style="font-weight: bold;">Edit line</span><span>,</span> disable those devices that should not trigger alarms (see chapter <a href="Config-sito__dettaglio_linea.htm">Line details</a>)</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="4">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Test field communications
                                                                                                 </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>After restarting the engine, the list of all field devices appears in <span style="font-weight: bold;">Global</span>.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="2">
                            <p>Check device status (in line, disconnected or disabled) and address (see chapter <a href="Monitoraggio__pagina_principale.htm">Monitoring: main page</a> )</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="5">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Printing the physical device list                                                                                                                            </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Global,</span> print the device list (see chapter <a href="Monitoraggio__pagina_principale.htm">Monitoring: main page</a>)</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="6">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Printing configuration settings
                                                                                                 </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">REPORT, Commissioning report  </span>print parameters (see chapter <a href="Report_collaudo__introduzione.htm">Print commissioning report</a>)</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="7">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Resetting alarms and events
                                                                                                 </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">System pages</span>, <span style="font-weight: bold;">System</span> cancel alarms and events generated during setup (see chapter <a href="Pagine_di_sistema-Remoto__stato_del_sistema.htm">System status</a>)</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <p>For further information, see chapter <a href="Configurazione__concetti_di_base.htm">Setup: basic concepts</a></p>
        <p class="TitoloInterno">
            <img src="../Resources/Images/AAaction.gif" style="border: none;float: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" /><a name="ProgrammareDispositivi"></a> Programming devices</p>
        <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="1">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Program device parameters
                                                                                                 </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;"> Global</span> double-click a device, <span style="font-weight: bold;">Parameters</span> page: set device parameters (see chapter <a href="Monitoraggio-dispositivo__parametri.htm">Setting device parameters</a>)</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="2">
                            <p>Propagating parameter settings on similar devices</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="TitoloInterno">
            <img src="../Resources/Images/AAaction.gif" style="border: none;float: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" /><a name="DefinireUtentiProfili"></a> Defining users and access profiles</p>
        <ol style="list-style: decimal;list-style-type: decimal;">
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="1">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Customizing login profiles
                                                                                                 </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">User configuration</span>, <span style="font-weight: bold;">Profiles</span> assign default users (Installer, Service, Users) group logon and editing permissions (see chapter <a href="Utenti_di_programma__profili_di_accesso.htm">Logon profiles</a>) </p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="2">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Define users and assign them default profiles
                                                                                                 </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">User configuration</span>, <span style="font-weight: bold;">Users</span> set typical users and assign them a default profile (installer, Service, User) specifying any restrictions for password expiry and maximum number of login attempts (see chapter <a href="Utenti_di_programma__utenti.htm">User configuration</a>).</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <p>For further information, see chapter <a href="Utenti_di_programma__concetti_di_base.htm">Program users: basic concepts</a></p>
        <p class="TitoloInterno">
            <img src="../Resources/Images/AAaction.gif" style="border: none;float: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" /><a name="ImpostareAttivtaSupervisione"></a> Setting supervision activities</p>
        <ol style="list-style: decimal;list-style-type: decimal;">
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="1">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Create HACCP and log report templates
                                                                                                 </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Periodic print configuration</span> define which reports will be printed at regular intervals (see chapter <a href="Report__introduzione.htm">Periodic report setup</a>).</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="2">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Follow the <a href="Procedure_creazione_attivita-locale.htm">Activity creation procedure</a> to define notification actions, field actions, print actions and warnings.</p>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <p>For further information, see chapter <a href="Attivita__concetti_di_base.htm">Activities basic concepts</a></p>
        <p class="TitoloInterno">
            <img src="../Resources/Images/AAaction.gif" style="border: none;float: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" /><a name="ConfigurareguardianPRO"></a>guardianPRO setup</p>
        <ol style="list-style: decimal;list-style-type: decimal;">
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="1">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Enable control on alarms that remain active
                                                                                                 </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Site setup, alarm safety </span> set the maximum notification time for each alarm priority (see chapter <a href="Config-sito__configurazione_priorita_allarmi.htm">Site setup: alarm priorities</a>).</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="2">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">System pages, guardianPRO  </span> enable the alarm control (see chapter <a href="Pagine_di_sistema__guardianPRO.htm">System setup guardianPRO</a>)</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="2">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Enable variable variation checks
                                                                                                 </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">System pages, guardianPRO  </span> enable probe variation checks and select variables (see chapter <a href="Pagine_di_sistema__guardianPRO.htm">System: guardianPRO setup</a>)</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="3">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Enable notifications on reserved channels
                                                                                                 </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>Create at least one privileged notification channel in <span style="font-weight: bold;">I/O configuration</span> for guardianPRO notifications adding addressees (see chapter <a href="Config-canali__introduzione.htm">Notification channel setup</a>)</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <table style="border-left-color: #000000;border-left-width: 1px;border-right-color: #000000;border-right-width: 1px;background-color: #c0c0c0;left: 0px;top: 38px;margin-left: 40px;width: 90%;border-spacing: 0px;" cellspacing="0" width="90%" bgcolor="#C0C0C0">
                        <col style="width: 6.855%;" />
                        <col style="width: 93.145%;" />
                        <tr valign="top">
                            <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 6.855%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-width: 2px;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-style: Solid;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" valign="middle" width="6.855%">
                                <p class="Note">
                                    <img src="../Resources/Images/AAtips.gif" style="border: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;float: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" />
                                </p>
                            </td>
                            <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 93.145%;padding-right: 1px;padding-left: 1px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 2px;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" width="93.145%">
                                <p>Always include a channel test contact.</p>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">System pages, guardianPRO  </span> enable notifications and select addressees (see chapter <a href="Pagine_di_sistema__guardianPRO.htm">System pages: guardianPRO</a>)</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="p-ActionDetail" value="4">
                <p class="ActionDetail">Test the channel 
                                                                                                 </p>
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">I/O configuration</span>, test all set notification channels selecting test contacts (see chapter <a href="Test_periferiche__introduzione.htm">Notifications-channels: test</a>).</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <table style="width: 100%;border-left-color: #000000;border-left-width: 1px;border-right-color: #000000;border-right-width: 1px;background-color: #c0c0c0;border-spacing: 0px;border-spacing: 0px;" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#C0C0C0" width="100%">
            <col style="width: 6.855%;" />
            <col style="width: 93.145%;" />
            <tr valign="top">
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 6.855%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-width: 2px;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-style: Solid;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" valign="middle" width="6.855%">
                    <p class="Note">
                        <img src="../Resources/Images/AAinfo.gif" style="border: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" />
                    </p>
                </td>
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 93.145%;padding-right: 1px;padding-left: 1px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 2px;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" width="93.145%">
                    <p>Restart the engine after changes.</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <p>For further information, see chapter <a href="guardianPRO__concetti_di_base.htm">guardianPRO: basic concepts</a></p>
